songs.title: This party is over
songs.lyrics:
This party is over now
Ho jao saare sober now x (3)

Bartender ko bolo ji
Aur na botal kholo ji
Apna sangi sathi dhoondho
Ab sab ghar ko ho lo ji

This party is over now
Ho jao saare sober now
This party is over now
Now now now now

Over now x (8)

Su chhe saaro chhi chhi
Gandi gandi daaru chhe x (3)

Su chhe saaro chhi chhi
Gandi gandi gandi gandi gandi

Bartender ko bolo ji
Aur na botal kholo ji
Apna sangi sathi dhoondho
Ab sab ghar ko ho lo ji

This party is over now
Ho jao saare sober now
This party is over now
Now now now now

Over now x (8)

Cham cham cham cham lights on
Aadhi janta ghar ko gone
Simple logon ki hai party
Na koyi gangster na koyi don

Nasha utaarne ke
Mere paas saare bhed hain
Party ho gayi over
Asuvidha ke liye khed hai
Jinko chadh gayi zyada
Unpe 500 ka zurmana
Anti alcoholic yeh hai
Yo yo ka Naya gana

Mitron, bekar ke shauk na paalo
Mitron, daaru pe nakhre na daalo
Mitron, youth ko samjha lo
Mitron, jaljeere se kaam chala lo

This party is over now
Ho jao saare sober now x (2)

Bartender ko bolo ji
Aur na botal kholo ji
Apna sangi sathi dhoondho
Ab sab ghar ko ho lo ji

This party is over now
Ho jao saare sober now
This party is over now
Now now now now

Dekheo dekho dekho yeh aaya kaun
Yo Yo Honey Singh!

Mitron, su chhe saaro chhi chhi
Gandi gandi daaru chhe x (4)

Yo Yo Honey Singh!

Mitron, mitron, mitron, mitron
Mitron!
